summary: Beautifully designed outdoor retreat in the Falkreath Hold for rangers, hunters, or wood elves. Plenty of storage/shelves/chests/bookshelves, vegetable garden, chopping block, cooking spit, smith crafting, enchanting, alchemy, and a stable for your horse and livestock.
descriptionHtml:
Beautifully designed outdoor retreat in the Falkreath Hold for rangers, hunters, or wood elves. Plenty of storage/shelves/chests/bookshelves, vegetable garden, chopping block, cooking spit, smith crafting, enchanting, alchemy, and a stable for your horse and livestock. 

I am adding the location on the map to the images to give you an idea of where it is located before you install, because I know there are a LOT of Falkreath house mods out there, and that can cause compatibility issues if they were built right on top of each other.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Check out my other player home mods: 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16143]Fire Dancer Retreat[/url] a mansion/manor in the reach with lots of features.

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16515]Windwood Redoubt[/url] a small fort for rouge characters. You can do what you want, be whoever you want, and you have excellent access to travelers on the road.  

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=17341]Caethspell Caverns[/url] a cave home for the druid nature/animal lover players. Includes a small indoor farm with livestock and crops - waterfall and pool, beautiful decor and scenery

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Troubleshooting
=================
Common issues:
-----------------------------
Problem:
Help! Grass is floating!
--
Solution: 
On skyrim.ini:
[Grass]
bAllowLoadGrass=0
bAllowCreateGrass=1
bDrawShaderGrass=1
----------------------------------
author: Cynster
